	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12">
			<div id="ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField1_label" style='display:none'></div><div id="ctl00_MainContentPlaceHolder_PageContentPlaceHolder_RichHtmlField1__ControlWrapper_OregonRichHtmlField" class="ms-rtestate-field" style="display:inline" ><span><h2 class="ms-rteElement-Heading2">Stay Connected</h2>
<div>We're committed to sharing information with our OrCPP members. News
 and announcements are sent through our email distribution list.<br><br></div>
<ul><li><a href="mailto&#58;info.orcpp@oregon.gov">Request to join our mailing list</a>
</li><li><a target="_blank" href="https&#58;//listsmart.osl.state.or.us/mailman/listinfo/orcpplink">General information about the mailing list</a></li><li><a href="mailto&#58;orcpplink-request@listsmart.osl.state.or.us">Unsubscribe or change your options</a></li></ul><div><br></div><h3 class="ms-rteElement-Heading3">Most Recent Emails&#58;</h3></span><div class="ms-rtestate-read ms-rte-wpbox"><div class="ms-rtestate-notify  ms-rtestate-read a1d24074-d8de-4a9a-be07-91b02ecec5e1" id="div_a1d24074-d8de-4a9a-be07-91b02ecec5e1" unselectable="on"><div id="MSOZoneCell_WebPartWPQ1" class="s4-wpcell-plain ms-webpartzone-cell ms-webpart-cell-vertical ms-fullWidth ">
	<div class="ms-webpart-chrome ms-webpart-chrome-vertical ms-webpart-chrome-fullWidth ">
	<div    id="WebPartWPQ1"  class="ms-WPBody "   style="" ><div id="ctl00_ctl40_g_a1d24074_d8de_4a9a_be07_91b02ecec5e1">
		<div class="list-unstyled panel-group or-accordion-list" id="accordion-ctl00_ctl40_g_a1d24074_d8de_4a9a_be07_91b02ecec5e1_ctl01">
			<div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-9f786a89-845d-47fc-b3d8-bed592f4cc7a">
				<h4>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#9f786a89-845d-47fc-b3d8-bed592f4cc7a" aria-controls="9f786a89-845d-47fc-b3d8-bed592f4cc7a" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="6e56c614-1239-46b0-b9d8-ad7aa046716b">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
							<div class="or-accordion-heading-title">
								<p class="panel-title">[orcpplink]School districts/schools food service products RFP S-10700-00015540 OregonBuys 02/27/2026</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h4><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="9f786a89-845d-47fc-b3d8-bed592f4cc7a" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClassA6A27CE12E9840B7A9825E236B4BD8D7"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">​Hello OrCPP
Community,<br></p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">DAS State
Procurement Services has an active Request for Proposals for Food Services
Products Price Agreements that includes the following Grocery categories&#58;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><ol type="1" style="direction&#58;ltr;unicode-bidi&#58;embed;margin-top&#58;0in;margin-bottom&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;"><li value="1" style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Shelf stable or dried goods</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Produce</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Dairy products</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Bakery (fresh and frozen</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Beverages </span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Seafood</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Meat </span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Small ware’s</span></li><li style="margin-top&#58;0px;margin-bottom&#58;0px;vertical-align&#58;middle;"><span style="font-size&#58;11pt;">Disposable ware</span></li></ol><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Suppliers can
provide broadline, truckload, or grocery by category, or grocery by region - by
category. </p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">These Price
Agreements will be available to all State Agencies, and OrCPP members including
schools, districts., correctional facilities, qualifying nonprofits and more.
The State of Oregon wants Suppliers large and small to propose!</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Please forward this
information to your food suppliers as they may not be registered on OregonBuys.
&#160;Interested Suppliers do not need to be registered in OregonBuys to view
the Bid Solicitation documents. </p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">OregonBuys
Link&#58;&#160; <a href="https&#58;//gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https&#58;//oregonbuys.gov/bso/&amp;data=05%7c02%7cKimberley.wisdom%40oregon.gov%7cf3cf76add7414bd10e5208de761c2f89%7caa3f6932fa7c47b4a0cea598cad161cf%7c0%7c0%7c639078060588039293%7cUnknown%7cTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7c0%7c%7c%7c&amp;sdata=uy8KAbcM5L%2B4%2ByVXyIouq5yF810RMSCsjx64rAyXGM0%3D&amp;reserved=0">https&#58;//oregonbuys.gov/bso/</a>
</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Bid Number&#58; <span style="background&#58;white;">S-10700-00015540</span></p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Single Point of
Contact&#58; Nancy Doll </p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Closing Date&#58;
4/9/2026 2&#58;30 PM<br></p></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-19689756-d27c-478f-9704-a9c1c7b58b1c">
				<h4>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#19689756-d27c-478f-9704-a9c1c7b58b1c" aria-controls="19689756-d27c-478f-9704-a9c1c7b58b1c" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="f3ae35b8-5fa7-4137-a38e-644b39040789">
