								<p class="panel-title">[orcpplink]Oregon Froward Program price agreement 8357 for temporary staffing services BlueSun, Inc. 02/23/2026</p>
							</div><span class="or-accordion-heading-collapse" role="img" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						</div>
					</div></button>
				</h4><div class="panel-collapse collapse" id="19689756-d27c-478f-9704-a9c1c7b58b1c" >
					<div class="panel-body">
						<div class="or-accordion-content-field">
							<div class="ExternalClass455A214392594FB197E577CC9BFBF2C2"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">​The Oregon Forward
Program is providing this courtesy notification to all Authorized Purchasers
regarding an update to Price Agreement 8357 for Temporary Staffing Services.<br></p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Amendment 11 has
been issued and includes the following changes&#58;</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Agreement
Changes&#58;</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Revised
Section 1 Agreement subsection 1.3 Agreement Documents, removed Attachment E
and Exhibit E-1 reference.</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Revised
Section 1 Agreement, subsection 1.9 VCAF and VSR</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Attachment
A - Product Pricing and Specifications </p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Added
Oregon State University specific positions</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Attachment
B – Schedule of Pricing</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Added
Oregon State University specific positions</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Attachment
D - Contact Information for the Parties</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Updated
contact details (Darvin Pierce retired effective 7/1/2025).</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Attachment
F – Contact Information for the Parties</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Updated
contact details (Darvin Pierce retired effective 7/1/2025).</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">All updated
documents, including Amendment 11, are available on OregonBuys under Price
Agreement 8357. Please refer to the “Attachments” tab to view the most current
version.</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">For more information
regarding this message, contact Rena Montes, Oregon Forward Program Contracts
Manager, at 503-507-1246 or via email <a href="mailto&#58;info.ofp@das.oregon.gov">info.ofp@das.oregon.gov</a>.<br></p></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-8a371352-7d8b-49d4-a191-1187818ebe00">
				<h4>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#8a371352-7d8b-49d4-a191-1187818ebe00" aria-controls="8a371352-7d8b-49d4-a191-1187818ebe00" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="5aa858c6-1b95-4f4f-acd7-122bf7e22131">
