							<div class="ExternalClass61E1F2798DCA4B9B9227CA7A9BB10CD9"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">​The Oregon Forward
Program is providing this courtesy notification to all Authorized Purchasers
regarding an update to Price Agreement PO-10700-00033258 for Security Service.<br></p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Amendment 20 has
