changes&#58; </p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Revised
Section 1 Agreement, subsection 1.3 Agreement Documents, removed Attachment E
and Exhibit E-1 reference.</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Revised
Section 1 Agreement, subsection VCAF and VSR</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Attachment
C - Insurance</p><p style="margin-top&#58;0pt;margin-bottom&#58;8pt;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">Updated
to reflect new insurance risk assessment review.</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">All updated
documents, including Amendment 20, are available on OregonBuys under Price
Agreement <a href="https&#58;//gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https&#58;//oregonbuys.gov/bso/external/purchaseorder/poSummary.sdo?docId%3DPO-10700-00033258%26releaseNbr%3D0%26external%3Dtrue%26parentUrl%3Dclose&amp;data=05%7c02%7cKimberley.wisdom%40oregon.gov%7c13e66bf1a3e44d1a777d08de70ce8413%7caa3f6932fa7c47b4a0cea598cad161cf%7c0%7c0%7c639072229467455123%7cUnknown%7cTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7c0%7c%7c%7c&amp;sdata=JT2ZYW8chy2n/G2/4zUZZvsF%2BV/dTOf%2BfWSzQo4zqTc%3D&amp;reserved=0">PO-10700-00033258</a>.
Please refer to the “Attachments” tab to view the most current version.</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">For more information
regarding this message, contact Rena Montes, Oregon Forward Program Contracts
Manager, at 503-507-1246 or via email <a href="mailto&#58;info.ofp@das.oregon.gov">info.ofp@das.oregon.gov</a><br></p></div>
