  Professional Inc</p></td><td style="border-width&#58;0pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;1.4388in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">PO-10700-00053650</p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width&#58;0pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;2.8354in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Harris
  &amp; Harris Ltd.</p></td><td style="border-width&#58;0pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;1.4388in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">PO-10700-00053647</p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width&#58;0pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;2.8354in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Linebarger
  Goggan Blair Sampson</p></td><td style="border-width&#58;0pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;1.4388in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">PO-10700-00053649</p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width&#58;0pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;2.8354in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Pioneer
  Credit Recovery Inc</p></td><td style="border-width&#58;0pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;1.4388in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">PO-10700-00053655</p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width&#58;0pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;2.8354in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Professional
  Credit</p></td><td style="border-width&#58;0pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;1.4388in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">PO-10700-00053648</p></td></tr><tr><td style="border-width&#58;0pt;vertical-align&#58;top;width&#58;2.8354in;padding&#58;4pt;"><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;color&#58;black;">Reliant
