">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">For more information
regarding this message, contact Nathan C. Ramos, Senior Contract Specialist, at
(971) 707-0016 or via email <a href="mailto&#58;Nathan.Ramos@DAS.Oregon.gov">Nathan.Ramos@DAS.Oregon.gov</a>.​<br></p></div>
