Program is sending this notification as a courtesy to all Authorized
Purchasers. Price Agreement 8275 for temporary staffing services has been
amended to extend the expiration date to February 6, 2030. </p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">The Price Agreement
amendment 12 and any documents related to the Price Agreement is now available
on OregonBuys (<a href="https&#58;//gcc02.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=https&#58;//oregonbuys.gov/bso/external/purchaseorder/poSummary.sdo?docId%3D8275%26releaseNbr%3D0%26external%3Dtrue%26parentUrl%3Dclose&amp;data=05%7c02%7cKimberley.wisdom%40oregon.gov%7c56dafb84605d43b49c4108de39ce53ec%7caa3f6932fa7c47b4a0cea598cad161cf%7c0%7c0%7c639011755494187607%7cUnknown%7cTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7c0%7c%7c%7c&amp;sdata=ojUgrptwMEhGNA3rLO2a977fbmX3Myaf0pRSw9lTSiA%3D&amp;reserved=0">8275</a>).
In OregonBuys refer to “Attachments” tab for the current Attachments.</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">&#160;</p><p style="margin&#58;0in;font-family&#58;calibri;font-size&#58;11pt;">For more information
regarding this message, contact Rena Montes, Oregon Forward Program Contracts
Manager, at 503-507-1246 or via email <a href="mailto&#58;info.ofp@das.oregon.gov">info.ofp@das.oregon.gov</a>
.<br></p></div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div><div class="panel panel-default or-accordion-panel" id="panel-724c73a1-d8fd-4a5b-8085-985ebdedcef5">
				<h4>
					<button class="collapsed btn btn-link or-accordion-panel-btn" href="#724c73a1-d8fd-4a5b-8085-985ebdedcef5" aria-controls="724c73a1-d8fd-4a5b-8085-985ebdedcef5" data-toggle="collapse" aria-expanded="false"><div class="panel-heading" id="40793dd4-a2f1-4d89-8b02-11594e999956">
						<div class="or-accordion-heading">
